  "description": "This individual is a cadaverous undead of human origin, reduced to a tight lattice of sinew over bone and marked by a fixed, death-rigid posture. Light skin lies cracked and parchment-dry across the face and hands, while gray eyes sit deep in the sockets with an unblinking, vitreous stare. Black hair persists in sparse, uneven clumps along the scalp, leaving the crown largely bare and emphasizing the pronounced brow and jaw. The body bears old joint distortions and chipped teeth consistent with long decay and repeated impact.",
